Archive a message (remove from inbox)

Usage: mxr archive [OPTIONS] [MESSAGE_ID]

Arguments:
  [MESSAGE_ID]  Message ID

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>  Operate on messages matching search query
      --yes              Skip confirmation
      --dry-run          Show what would happen
  -h, --help             Print help
